    <div class="faq-area ptb-100">
        <h1 style="text-align: center;">FAQs for study MBBS in Georgia 2023</h1>
            <div class="container">
                
                
                <div class="faq-accordion accordion" id="faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;">  Is MBBS admission in Georgia decided based on the NEET score?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>The Indian Medical Council requires NEET exams for all MBBS admissions of Indian students, both inside and outside India. However, candidates must achieve a minimum NEET score in order to apply for MBBS admission in Georgia and other countries. </p>
                               
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;"> What is the Accommodation and Hostel facilities available for MBBS Students?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Indian students have not faced any problems when it comes to finding decent accommodation in Georgia. Most universities offer on-campus hostel facilities for students. Most hostels have kitchen facilities where students can cook their own meals. </p>
                                
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;">What is the Fee Structure of Medical Colleges in Georgia?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>The tuition fees for most medical institutions in Georgia range from $ 4,000 to $ 8,000. The cost of the hostel is about $ 250- $ 300. </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;"> Is MBBS from Georgia university valid for practice in India?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>MCI is aware of most medical institutions in Georgia. Bachelor's degrees from these institutions are valid for practice in India. Their only requirement is that they be subject to MCI screening tests. </p>
                               
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;"> Can I practice or look for a job in Georgia, after completing my MBBS from Georgia?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Yes, in fact, some of the best multinationals are based in Georgia, offering both internships and jobs to MBBS graduates. </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSix" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;">  Apart from India, where else can I practice with my Georgian MBBS degree?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>All MBBSs who have graduated from a Georgian university can practice in the country of their choice as long as they pass the proficiency test in that country. In the United States, the proficiency test is USMLE. PLAB in the UK. Similarly, in Australia it is AMC. In European countries, you need to take a language proficiency test and a practical license test for that country. </p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse7" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse7">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;">What’s the medium/language of teaching in Georgia?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse7" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>English is the medium of instruction for international students . </p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse8" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;">Do Indian students suffer any language barrier while studying MBBS in Georgia?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse8" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>All the younger generation in Georgia speak good English and can effectively interact with international students without hiccups. Therefore, Indian students do not suffer from language barriers while in Georgia.</p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse9" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;"> Are there really no tests like IELTS and TOEFL to qualify for MBBS admission in Georgia?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse9" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Many universities do not require TOEFL or IELTS. However, some institutions require you to qualify for one of these tests. </p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse10" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;">  Are there any scholarships for meritorious students? </h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse10" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>No. However, students do have performance-related grants. The scholarship covers tuition and hostel fees and is a scholarship for all practical purposes. </p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse11" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;">Which are the best medical universities to study MBBS in Georgia?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse11" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>University of Georgia, Akaki Tsereteli State University, Batumi international university and much more</p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse12" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;">  What is the period to complete the whole MBBS course in Georgia?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse12" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Georgia MBBS degrees are completed within 5.8 years, including a one-year internship. </p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse13" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;">  What age students are allowed to study MBBS in Georgia?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse13" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>You must be at least 17 years old to study MBBS in Georgia with a capping of 25 years old. </p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                   <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse14" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;"> How many Indian students are studying in Georgia?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse14" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Approximately 2000 Indian students’ study in Georgia, and 500 students from various universities enrol in MBBS each year. </p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div> 
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" 
                                data-bs-target="#collapse15" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;"> Is the exam pattern for MBBS in Georgia yearly or semester wise?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse15" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>MBBS course in Georgia, students are required to earn credits in the grade evaluation system and take the annual exam.  
	</p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapse16" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;"> Is Georgia MBBS degree valid in India?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse16" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Yes, it is valid in India if you have a bachelor's degree from a university accredited by the Medical Council of India.   
	</p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapse17" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                  <h2 style="font-size:19px;">    Is it compulsory to learn the Georgian language?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse17" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>No, learning Georgian is not mandatory because the medium of education is English, but it is a good idea to learn if needed as it simplifies daily life and communication with local patients and other locals.    
	</p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapse18" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;">  I have heard the Indian embassy is not available in Georgia. Is that so?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse18" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Yes, the Embassy of India is not available in Georgia. The Embassy of India is located in Yerevan, Armenia. It is assigned there to take care of the problems, incidents, documents, and errands of all kinds of Indians living in Georgia and Armenia. After landing, it is advisable to register the student's name with the Indian Embassy in Armenia. 
	</p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapse19" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;">  Is MCI/FMGE coaching available?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse19" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Yes, MCI / FMGE coaching is offered at all MCI accredited universities.  
	</p>
                              
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
