                            <h2 style="font-size:19px;">  Is Georgia a safe country for the students to study?</h2>
                        </button>
                        <div id="collapse20" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>Yes, Georgia is a safe country for students to study MBBS. No such criminal record was found in Georgia.
